{"tid":1460752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"去機場接機唔會告暴動罪","createTime":"2019-08-13T04:41:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:31:41.000Z","uid":53000,"like":25,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a1242f82bb14dee48d6bf6bf7261ee83e902cf81","tid":1460752,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:41:54.000Z","msg":"一來冇衝擊<br />\n二來如果定性為暴動<br />\n全部 cancel / delay 航班冇得 claim 保險<br />\n全球來往香港嘅航班旅客都冇得 claim<br />\n<br />\n接機睇 IMAX有用過勇武衝擊同堵路，<br />\n又唔會俾人話擾民，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">記得唔好帶 gear 唔好著黑衫<br />\n著到色彩繽紛</span><br />\n就冇人知邊啲係旅客，邊啲係示威者,<br />\n見到有人想衝擊，即刻㩒低佢，<br />\n取消哂航班之後散水<br />\n復航之後再去接機睇 IMAX<br />\n<br />\n清場之前要走,<br />\n停飛，佢會疏散旅客，<br />\n嗰陣扮旅客一齊走<br />\n所以唔好著黑衫<br />\n除非佢癲到拘捕旅客<br />\n或者旅客未走哂之前放催淚彈<br />\n<br />\n用左 過千人受傷<br />\n幾百人被捕<br />\n六十幾日<br />\n七條人命<br />\n一隻眼<br />\n換返嚟嘅皇牌<br />\n最終摸索得出嘅方法<br />\n一定要珍惜"},{"pid":"5d5b1cb48c3b75278b194dae1852d499d136cc64","tid":1460752,"uid":41584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:42:14.000Z","msg":"對付林鄭，要草船借箭<br />\n催淚彈已經係常餐，會唔會有手足去禮賓府開餐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451531</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0ed7132659fb0cdbbebd54b200f27971d2523523","tid":1460752,"uid":294974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:42:33.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得講得啱，唔該睇睇同幫推唔該<br />\np牌仔嘅野冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(話我鬼都要講㗎喇)佔機場唔係無撚敵㗎，屌<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dDbQKT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dDbQKT</a>"},{"pid":"ab1899d1ffd7cf9f68b6573888b175767e375007","tid":1460752,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:42:46.000Z","ms